<item>
            <title>[WICKET-3745] AbstractSingleSelectChoice tries to convert the input using the id generated by IChoiceRenderer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-3745</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If one set a type for an AbstractSingleSelectChoice component, it will start to get error because the input being converted to model type was not generated by the converter, but by the IChoiceRenderer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12508476">WICKET-3745</key>
